Installation instruction for tar.gz package
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Before install this program please install Raspberry Pi OS to SD-CARD.
Do not forget to set hostname and network and enable SPI module.

Installation
------------
  $ tar -xzf mm5d-sw-0.6-armhf.tar.gz
  $ cd mm5d-sw
  $ sudo raspi-config
  $ ./prepare
  $ ./install

Set program
-----------
  $ mm5d-editmainconf

Set environment characteristics
-------------------------------
  $ mm5d-editenvirconf

Removing
--------
  $ cd mm5d-sw
  $ ./uninstall

